<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:57:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>官方媒体称，中国提供了额外的自然灾害救助资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</link><description>据官方媒体周四报道，中国已向几个受洪水影响的省份提供了 4.96 亿元人民币（6826 万美元）的额外自然灾害救助资金，以帮助紧急救援以及灾民的搬迁和安置。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:53:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>美元坚挺，日元受创接近数十年低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/battered-yen-pinned-near-multi-decade-low-amid-resilient-dollar-2024-06-27/</link><description>周四，日元跌至 38 年低点附近，并在 1 美元兑 160 日元的弱势区间徘徊，这让市场对日本当局采取干预措施支撑日元的任何迹象保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:30:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/battered-yen-pinned-near-multi-decade-low-amid-resilient-dollar-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：通胀恐慌和日元空头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-26/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 21:51:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾大使没有在中国争端中寻求美国的补给支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</link><description>菲律宾驻华盛顿大使周三表示，在与中国在有争议的南中国海的对峙中，菲律宾尚未请求美国支持为其军队提供补给，并补充说美国只是提供援助菲律宾的“视觉”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，波音公司恢复向中国交付宽体飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resuming-widebody-airplane-deliveries-china-source-says-2024-06-26/</link><description>据知情人士透露，波音公司正在恢复向中国供应宽体喷气式飞机，该项目最近几周因中国监管审查而暂停。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:24:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resuming-widebody-airplane-deliveries-china-source-says-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国进口关税提高，沃尔沃将推迟 EX30 在美国的发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-delay-ex30s-us-shipments-due-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-bloomberg-news-2024-06-26/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车发言人周三表示，在中国出口关税上调后，沃尔沃汽车将推迟在美国交付 EX30 电动汽车，因为该公司专注于扩大中国以外紧凑型 SUV 的生产。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 19:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-delay-ex30s-us-shipments-due-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-bloomberg-news-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>据《Information》报道，亚马逊将推出从中国直接发货的折扣专区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-launch-discount-section-with-direct-shipping-china-information-reports-2024-06-26/</link><description>据《The Information》周三报道，亚马逊计划在其购物网站上推出一个专区，专门销售廉价商品，这些商品可从中国的仓库直接运送给海外消费者，并援引向中国卖家展示的幻灯片。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 17:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-launch-discount-section-with-direct-shipping-china-information-reports-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁试图通过工业园激励措施吸引比亚迪汽车工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/peru-trying-lure-byd-auto-plant-with-industrial-park-incentive-2024-06-26/</link><description>秘鲁总统周三会见了中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪，邀请高管在这个安第斯国家的太平洋沿岸开设工厂，另一家中国公司正在那里建设一个大型港口，以促进两国之间的贸易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 16:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/peru-trying-lure-byd-auto-plant-with-industrial-park-incentive-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>印度给予玉米、植物油进口关税优惠</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-allows-imports-corn-vegetable-oils-concessional-duty-2024-06-26/</link><description>印度周三在关税配额（TRQ）下允许有限进口玉米、葵花籽油、精炼菜籽油和奶粉，进口商支付零关税或较低关税，以降低食品通胀。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:27:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-allows-imports-corn-vegetable-oils-concessional-duty-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>德中签署数据共享声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-declaration-data-sharing-2024-06-26/</link><description>德国一位部长周三表示，德国和中国已经签署了一份关于如何讨论跨境数据传输的意向声明，这是汽车制造商能够向德国传输数据的又一步。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:28:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-declaration-data-sharing-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>英国人权组织发起运动阻止 Shein 潜在的伦敦首次公开募股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-human-rights-group-launches-campaign-stop-sheins-potential-london-ipo-2024-06-26/</link><description>代表该组织的一家律师事务所周三表示，总部位于英国的人权组织“制止维吾尔族种族灭绝”已发起一项法律运动，以阻止 Shein 可能在伦敦上市，原因是对其劳工行为的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-human-rights-group-launches-campaign-stop-sheins-potential-london-ipo-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国在南海拦截了美国飞机投放的潜艇探测器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-intercepts-submarine-probe-dropped-us-aircraft-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国国家电视台央视旗下社交媒体帐户“愚园探天”周三称，中国最近拦截了一架美国军机投放到南海的潜艇探测器。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 11:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-intercepts-submarine-probe-dropped-us-aircraft-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>中方驳斥美国特使有关阻碍人文交流的言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-us-envoys-comment-that-it-hinders-people-to-people-exchanges-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国外交部称美国大使尼古拉斯·伯恩斯周三的言论“牵强”，称其偏离了两国总统达成的重要谅解。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-us-envoys-comment-that-it-hinders-people-to-people-exchanges-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>体操——日本男子最高目标击败中国夺得团体金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-japanese-mens-top-goal-is-beating-china-team-gold-2024-06-26/</link><description>在距 2020 年东京奥运会男子体操团体冠军仅一步之遥的情况下，日本队决心在巴黎奥运会上击败最大的对手中国队夺得金牌，并将其作为他们的首要任务，距离奥运会开幕还有一个月的时间。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 07:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-japanese-mens-top-goal-is-beating-china-team-gold-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商世茂清算听证会延期至7月31日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-july-31-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国房地产开发商世茂集团周三在一份文件中表示，该公司再次延长了债权人有关债务重组计划的最后期限，该公司的清算案已推迟至 7 月 31 日。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-july-31-2024-06-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>